---
import ZhProductLayout from '../../../../layouts/ZhProductLayout.astro';
---

<ZhProductLayout title="CNC翼型连接块 | DGSDK 史帝克"
  description="高精度CNC铣削翼型连接块，用于工业设备结构连接和精密装配系统集成。"
  image="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-wing-connection-block.jpg">
  <section class="product-detail-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/zh/">首页</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/zh/products">产品</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts">精密加工零件</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span>CNC翼型连接块</span>
      </div>

      <div class="product-top">
        <div class="product-gallery">
          <div class="product-main-image slider-wrapper">
            <button class="slider-arrow left" id="prevImage">‹</button>
            <img
              id="mainProductImage"
              src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-wing-connection-block.jpg"
              alt="CNC翼型连接块"
            />
            <button class="slider-arrow right" id="nextImage">›</button>
          </div>

          <div class="product-thumbs">
            <img
              class="thumb-image active-thumb"
              src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-wing-connection-block.jpg"
              alt="CNC翼型连接块缩略图"
              data-full="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-wing-connection-block.jpg"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="product-summary">
          <h1>CNC翼型连接块</h1>
          <p class="product-short-desc">
            高精度CNC铣削翼型连接块，用于工业设备结构连接和精密装配系统集成。
          </p>

          <div class="product-actions">
            <button class="quote-btn" type="button">获取报价</button>
            <a href="https://wa.me/61436605126" target="_blank" class="whatsapp-btn">WhatsApp</a>
          </div>

          <div class="product-highlights">
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>精密连接</h4>
              <p>高精度加工，确保结构连接的精准性和可靠性。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>CNC铣削</h4>
              <p>精密CNC铣削工艺，尺寸公差控制严格。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>结构可靠</h4>
              <p>优质材料加工，连接稳固，适合工业长期使用。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>产品描述</h2>
        <p>
          CNC翼型连接块是工业自动化设备和精密装配系统中的重要结构零件，用于连接和固定设备的各个功能模块。
        </p>
        <p>
          采用高精度CNC铣削工艺加工，严格控制尺寸精度和表面质量，确保连接可靠、装配精准，满足工业设备的结构强度和精度要求。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>产品特点</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>高精度CNC铣削加工，公差控制严格</li>
          <li>翼型结构设计，连接稳固可靠</li>
          <li>适用于工业设备模块连接</li>
          <li>优质材料，耐用性强</li>
          <li>支持定制尺寸和规格</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>技术优势</h2>
        <div class="advantage-grid">
          <div class="advantage-card blue">
            <h3>精密加工</h3>
            <p>高精度CNC铣削确保连接块的尺寸精度和装配可靠性。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-card yellow">
            <h3>结构稳固</h3>
            <p>翼型连接设计，提供可靠的结构支撑和连接强度。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-card green">
            <h3>耐用可靠</h3>
            <p>优质材料和精密工艺，满足工业设备长期稳定使用。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>应用行业</h2>
        <div class="application-tags">
          <span>CNC加工</span>
          <span>精密制造</span>
          <span>工业设备</span>
          <span>自动化设备</span>
          <span>机械零件</span>
          <span>OEM生产</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <div class="related-slider-wrap" data-current="cnc-wing-connection-block">
          <div class="related-slider-header">
            <h2>相关产品</h2>
            <div class="related-slider-nav">
              <button class="related-slider-btn related-slider-prev" type="button">‹</button>
              <button class="related-slider-btn related-slider-next" type="button">›</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="related-slider-track">
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/custom-precision-machined-parts" class="related-slide-card" data-key="custom-precision-machined-parts">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-machined-parts.jpg" alt="定制精密加工零件" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>定制精密加工零件</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-front-panel-rubber-roller-assembly" class="related-slide-card" data-key="cnc-milled-front-panel-rubber-roller-assembly">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-front-panel-rubber-roller-assembly.jpg" alt="CNC铣削前面板橡胶辊组件" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>CNC铣削前面板橡胶辊组件</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/cnc-wing-connection-block" class="related-slide-card" data-key="cnc-wing-connection-block">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/cnc-milled-wing-connection-block.jpg" alt="CNC翼型连接块" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>CNC翼型连接块</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/lathe-machined-bearing-outer-retainer-plate" class="related-slide-card" data-key="lathe-machined-bearing-outer-retainer-plate">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/lathe-machined-bearing-outer-retainer-plate.jpg" alt="车床加工轴承外圆固定板" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>车床加工轴承外圆固定板</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/lathe-machined-shaft-end-fixing-component" class="related-slide-card" data-key="lathe-machined-shaft-end-fixing-component">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/lathe-machined-shaft-end-fixing-component.jpg" alt="车床加工轴端固定件" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>车床加工轴端固定件</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/milled-front-inner-fixing-plate-paper-roll-guide-rail" class="related-slide-card" data-key="milled-front-inner-fixing-plate-paper-roll-guide-rail">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/milled-front-inner-fixing-plate-paper-roll-guide-rail.jpg" alt="铣削前内固定板纸卷导轨" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>铣削前内固定板纸卷导轨</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled" class="related-slide-card" data-key="precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled.jpg" alt="精密轴承支架（CNC铣削）" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>精密轴承支架（CNC铣削）</h4>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</ZhProductLayout>
